These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, reading, woodworking, writing
There 5 different types of food: papaya, eggplant, apple, radish, cabbage
5 different games are played: chess, poker, billiard, go, monopoly
 1. the person eating papaya is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person playing chess##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is between the person eating papaya and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
 8. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 9. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the person eating cabbage is the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
12. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | dancing    | reading  | writing | cooking    | woodworking |
| Food   | eggplant     | apple   | radish | cabbage | papaya   |
| Game         | chess | poker | go  | monopoly | billiard        |

