.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, disco, salsa, punk, dubstep
City: venice, san-francisco, hamburg, new-york, liverpool
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 5. the fan of disco is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
11. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is handball##2
12. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | disco         | reggae | dubstep        | salsa   |
| City     | san-francisco | hamburg | new-york  | liverpool | venice |
| Sport   | lacrosse       | water-polo      | swimming   | handball           | golf      |

