.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, amaryllis, marigold, daffodil
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rugby, skateboarding, swimming
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, house, reggae, soul, d&b
 1. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the fan of house is the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 5. the person who growslily is between the fan of house and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 6. the fan of reggae is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of d&b##1
11. the person who's sport is basketball is the fan of reggae##1
12. the fan of soul is between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Flower    | amaryllis | daisy    | marigold   | lily          | daffodil      |
| Sport       | rugby    | swimming | golf       | skateboarding | basketball |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | soul     | house | indie          | reggae     |

