.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
There 5 different types of food: peach, apple, lime, lemon, onion
5 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, rose, sunflower, aconite, dahlia
 1. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 3. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 5. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
11. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| Food   | peach     | onion    | lime  | lemon | apple |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat    | hamster | mouse  | bird    |
| Flower     | dahlia      | sunflower | aconite    | rose    | amaryllis    |

